WEBVTT

1
00:06:37.380 --> 00:06:38.890 
沙祖
Zazu...

2
00:06:39.710 --> 00:06:42.060 
你害得我丢掉了午餐
you've made me lose my lunch.

3
00:06:42.300 --> 00:06:44.130 
你错过了早上的仪式
You will answer to Mufasa

4
00:06:44.130 --> 00:06:45.680 
要向木法沙回话
for missing the ceremony this morning.

5
00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:47.690 
我不会向任何人回话
I answer to no one.

6
00:06:49.430 --> 00:06:52.220 
疤面  疤面  疤面
Scar? Scar. Scar.

7
00:06:52.220 --> 00:06:54.520 
别  别这么看着我
No, no. Don't look at me like that.

8
00:06:54.520 --> 00:06:56.650 
你饿吗  沙祖
Are you hungry, Zazu?

9
00:06:56.980 --> 00:06:59.950 
要不要和我一起吃个饭
Perhaps we could have a bite together!

10
00:07:01.230 --> 00:07:02.150 
你不能吃我
You can't eat me!

11
00:07:02.150 --> 00:07:06.250 
禁止捕食王宫成员
It is forbidden to eat a member of the king's court!

12
00:07:06.280 --> 00:07:08.570 
不  求你了  住手
No, please! Stop it!

